# Title: Powershell Inline Execution From A File
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-12-25
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects inline execution of PowerShell code from a file
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_powershell_exec_data_file.yml

CommandLine IN ("*iex *", "*Invoke-Expression *", "*Invoke-Command *", "*icm *") CommandLine="* -raw*" CommandLine IN ("*cat *", "*get-content *", "*type *")